Reviews: I love the creativity.  I found this place whilst scrolling through IG and knew I had to try it.  I'll be honest that I wasn't a fan of the noodles inside the quesadilla but I will say that it tasted very much like pho w/ the addition of the tortilla.    The BBH burrito blew my mind on the other hand.  This was spicy and the broth that came w/ it acted like a dipping sauce but it didn't need it.  The burrito wasn't dry - tasted bomb on its own.  I will come back to order 5 of these.    BTW - word has it that they have tamales now!  Check this place out on IG and try it for yourself.  Now more than ever it's important to not only eat well, be happy, and support local businesses!
Replies: Bullet points: - Noodles inside the quesadilla were not preferred by the user. - Quesadilla tasted like pho with the addition of the tortilla. - BBH burrito was highly appreciated by the user. - Burrito was spicy and not dry, and tasted great even without the dipping sauce.

Summary: Based on the provided bullet points, it seems that there are mixed reviews about Quarantine Express's food quality and staff behavior. Let's start with the positive points. One user highly appreciated the BBH burrito, stating that it was spicy and not dry, and tasted great even without the dipping sauce. Additionally, the user found the burrito to be highly enjoyable. However, there were some negative points brought up as well. One user did not prefer the noodles inside the quesadilla, and mentioned that it tasted like pho with the addition of the tortilla. This may indicate a lack of cohesion in the dish's flavors. Another user found the food to be just "fine", which is not a particularly glowing review. Furthermore, there were complaints about unprofessional behavior from staff. This can be a significant issue, as it can greatly impact a customer's experience at the restaurant. It's important for staff to be friendly, helpful, and respectful towards their customers. In summary, Quarantine Express's food quality has received mixed reviews, with some dishes being highly appreciated and others receiving lackluster responses. Additionally, there have been complaints about staff behavior.
